GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from 6th July, 2022:
Shri Mukhtar Abbas Naqvi relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Minority Affairs;
MOST IMMEDIATE
Shri Ramchandra Prasad Singh relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Steel;
SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 6th July, 2022
Smt. Smriti Zubin Irani assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
Minority Affairs. She will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of
Women and Child Development; and
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Shri Jyotiraditya M. Scindia assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
Steel. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Civil
Aviation.
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
Copy also forwarded for information to :
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
